==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Moon-eye
<hw>Moon"-eye`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A eye
affected by the moon; also, a disease in the eye of a horse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>Any species of
American fresh-water fishes of the genus <gen>Hyodon</gen>, esp.
<spn>Hyodon tergisus</spn> of the Great Lakes and adjacent waters.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>The cisco.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moon-eyed</ent>⟦br⟧
